public static String[] split(String text,
                             String delim)
Splits text to a string array according to provided delimiter. Delimiter has to be StringTokenizer delimiter. If either text or delim is null, the method returns string array with length 0.

mergeStringArrays

public static String[] mergeStringArrays(String[][] arrayOfArrays)
Merges an array of string arrays to a concatenated string array. Concatenation is done in the following order arrayOfArrays[0][0],arrayOfArrays[0][1] ... arrayOfArrays[1][0] ... arrayOfArrays[x][z] if arrayOfArrays is null the method return string array with length 0. any null value in arrayOfArrays is skipped.
